# Project Autopilot Manager

## Purpose

Run large project tasks through durable docs and bounded fresh-session phases so Codex can keep working without rescanning the entire codebase every time.

## Core Guarantees

- Keep atlas docs current after code changes.
- Store project memory in files, not chat memory.
- Split large work into bounded phases.
- Generate fresh-session prompts automatically.
- Work across different local projects by changing the target project path.

## Main Script
